Definition: shrub with white woolly branches and woolly leaves having fragrant flowers forming long sprays
Example: flowers suitable for drying; sometimes placed in genus Helichrysum
Synonyms: Ozothamnus_secundiflorus, Helichrysum_secundiflorum, everlasting, genus_Ozothamnus, m, shrub, with, white, woolly, branches, and, leaves, having, fragrant, flowers, forming, long, sprays, suitable, for, drying, sometimes, placed, in, genus, Helichrysum
Category: noun.plant
